  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to gather stool samples from subjects with
      inflammatory bowel disease (IBD) to be added to a test set of stool samples that will be
      utilized to help select molecular markers and determine the optimal sensitivity and
      specificity values for the Exact IBD-ACRN surveillance test for colorectal cancer (CRC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
